description: This file contains unit tests for the UserSettings component, including setup of mock objects, verification of method existence, and test cases for setting and getting various user configuration parameters using Google Test and Google Mock frameworks.

classes.name: UserSettingsTest
classes.description: Test fixture class for initializing and cleaning up mocks and components used in UserSettings unit tests.

methods.name: UserSettingsTest
methods.description: Constructor initializing the test environment, setting up mock behavior, and initializing the plugin.

methods.name: ~UserSettingsTest
methods.description: Destructor cleaning up allocated resources and deinitializing the plugin.

methods.name: RegisteredMethods
methods.description: Test that all expected method identifiers exist in the handler.

methods.name: SetAudioDescription_Failure
methods.description: Test case verifying failure response for setAudioDescription method when mock returns error.

methods.name: SetAudioDescription_Success
methods.description: Test case verifying successful setAudioDescription operation.

methods.name: GetAudioDescription_Failure
methods.description: Test case verifying failure response for getAudioDescription method.

methods.name: GetAudioDescription_Success
methods.description: Test case verifying successful getAudioDescription operation.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_Failure
methods.description: Failure for setVoiceGuidanceRate, including out of range validations.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureOutOfRangeMin
methods.description: Failure when rate is below minimum allowed (less than 0.02).

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureOutOfRangeMax
methods.description: Failure when rate exceeds maximum allowed (greater than 10.99).

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_Success
methods.description: Success scenario for setVoiceGuidanceRate with valid input.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceHints_Failure
methods.description: Failure for setting voice guidance hints.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceHints_Success
methods.description: Success for setting voice guidance hints.

methods.name: SetContentPin_SuccessWithEmptyString
methods.description: Successful setting content pin with empty string.

methods.name: SetContentPin_Failure
methods.description: Failure in setting content pin due to mock returning error.

methods.name: SetContentPin_FailureWithAlphanumericInput
methods.description: Invalid parameter error when contentPin contains non-numeric characters.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureThreeDigitNumber
methods.description: Invalid parameter error when rate has three digits.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureFiveDigitNumber
methods.description: Invalid parameter error when rate has five digits.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureAllSpecialCharacters

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureWithOneSpecialCharacter
methods.description: Invalid parameter error when rate contains one special character.

methods.name: SetVoiceGuidanceRate_FailureSpecialCharactersAndDecimal
methods.description: Invalid parameter error for complex special characters in rate.

methods.name: GetContentPin_Failure
methods.description: Failure response when getContentPin returns error.

methods.description: Failure in getMigrationState method when mock returns error.
